{"tid":1502434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有成千個勇武見到十幾隻速龍都要退？","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T11:10:59.000Z","uid":43557,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c13b69d3358e06c05603e1eba43cea772538d285","tid":1502434,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔衝一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d4484ed30c960a352d54d5e5b2e6ac50914453","tid":1502434,"uid":98842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">【無人講 我講】機場=春袋 建議每個禮拜六日都去<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502397</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ffd408ca58049f18c41a14d75b482112b349c2c","tid":1502434,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a634f7b7fff55502d77f75e349567c424c248b7e","tid":1502434,"uid":21139,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"幾時先可以克服到恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係當你唔再執著某件事嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad546fb3838cd2f87929b8412b1459a5e47f20f9","tid":1502434,"uid":181778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06fc1baa00c10b64473c126153973ec946feb29a","tid":1502434,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaccbf572b29f865bb173b4a4673568cf5c5404","tid":1502434,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"713cb852b0a39ed26eedf32e5964eac7f078ad49","tid":1502434,"uid":61520,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"我地今場運動證明左好多野，<br />\n證明左中聯辦治港<br />\n證明左警黑合作<br />\n證明左武警扮黑警<br />\n證明黑警會扮示威者<br />\n證明左狗鐵監控直駁狗總<br />\n再俾你地證明監控燈柱直駁大陸<br />\n仲證明左好多野！<br />\n然後呢？沒有然係，證明咁多野做咩？ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢場運動唔係捉錯處，唔係搵得越多就會贏。港共根本一步一步謀殺緊香港人。</span></span><br />\n場運動根本入左死局，示威者剩係識不停漫無目的咁上街示威，白白犧牲，然後港共就加強打壓。<br />\n咁樣係唔會贏架！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只有撃中港共弱點，先有資格同佢平起平坐講數。</strong></span></span><br />\n只有港共一跪，所有野先有機會平反，要撒監控唔係去發現佢監控，然後推低支燈柱，係要去解決個源頭，否則我地同大陸人有咩分別？<br />\n大陸人一樣知中共幾醜惡，但佢地推翻唔到，證明到個政府有幾邪惡係無用架！<br />\n明明已經有咁清晰嘅弱點暴露左出黎，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>機場就係港共春袋</strong></span></span><br />\n唔去打佢痛處，依然每星期動員去上街，叫叫口號拍拍手散水就可以？<br />\n然後再俾人捉幾十人去審？<br />\n經濟唔肯犧牲，時間唔肯犧牲，<br />\n旅客都唔可以犧牲。<br />\n咁只好犧牲我地年輕一代，犧牲佢地健康，<br />\n犧牲佢地健全，最後犧牲佢地性命先滿足？"},{"pid":"6e3a73d7d5902698adb1f2439d2f36c0e3c37a9d","tid":1502434,"uid":197379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5b57e6d10409f357da3f56e28c5b2ffda0d08b9","tid":1502434,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b967717f1960146dd350c72d23ad94cb37a0c72","tid":1502434,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手推<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴叫大家星期一入機場啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501202</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔使嘈幾時入機場啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一入機場（圍國泰城）</span></span>"},{"pid":"26bdf788adddf7b94bde1c41e3ba5164b2c22a71","tid":1502434,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"其實大家都唔敢還拖，咁不如全力all in機場"},{"pid":"fffa9c3ec96a15dcafa8607e135db3624f60d5f1","tid":1502434,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a634f7b7fff55502d77f75e349567c424c248b7e","tid":1502434,"uid":21139,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"幾時先可以克服到恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係當你唔再執著某件事嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"講就講係前線 但其實大家都擔心比人捉到既後果 驚好合理"},{"pid":"9463ff7dab443fb2e87f382bf4d7bcb68d0ac864","tid":1502434,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"救人"},{"pid":"5ac746d20f54837292a19c48050a483652f3cfe0","tid":1502434,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"一定有人唔敢還拖的原因係因為驚得自己一個還拖，變左送頭。身邊個個都跑，自己走去還拖，如果比人賣咁點？根本冇人知身邊人夠唔夠膽還拖"},{"pid":"3f51d6f9a61bdb525ced8ea1d2d6bf96e1454867","tid":1502434,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"自己做唔到嘅野 我唔會要求人地做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9acbf665d0be3700b63fc0e1098468c61dbae8","tid":1502434,"uid":304306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"其實都講左好耐<br />\n200萬人出得黎 咁支持者9成9係再乘1.5到<br />\n大概300萬人<br />\n而狗係得30000隻<br />\n單純人數黎睇係無得輸<br />\n衰啲講句9個做砲灰 剩返1個點都咬得甩佢春袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事實就係大家始終係普通人<br />\n無諗住要真係打人甚至殺人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最少條底線就係頂住可以但唔可以傷到人<br />\n<br />\n但係啲狗就唔同<br />\n佢地係出黎打人兼夾當食雞<br />\n打中加兩分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 殺一個加十分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捉到啲靚妹就的返去差館扣佢五十分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果話要贏<br />\n可能真係要等到佢地變成同狗一樣GE思想先有可能做到<br />\n但係人狗殊途 <br />\n話做就做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b615ef4653a714a3e53091c6be2196d78f66af1e","tid":1502434,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:34:58.000Z","msg":"有撚咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線有啲只係食花生<br />\n再講<br />\n你真係要team up 幾個先可以共同進退<br />\n好多時你以為上<br />\n點知身邊個個退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457ad92e114bf6968fdf0f290d67df0bf2c606b3","tid":1502434,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"九成係花生前線 So99y<br />\n真武勇見到十個有九個花生友走左都局退啦"},{"pid":"0ccf07908a7c3d5872becd370752d8196f969ad5","tid":1502434,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c13b69d3358e06c05603e1eba43cea772538d285","tid":1502434,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔衝一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"個個都瘦底 排骨仔<br />\n點夠人打 <br />\n又有槍<br />\n你咩都無<br />\n比人捉左<br />\n男既死<br />\n女既大肚<br />\n點玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你落場囉"}]}